-- Statkraft of Norway to Invest $400 Million in Peruvian Hydropower Plant
-- B y   M a r i a n n e   S t i g s e t
-- 2010-09-30T07:19:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/statkraft-of-norway-to-invest-400-million-in-peruvian-hydropower-plant.html
Statkraft AS will invest in the
hydropower plant Cheves in Peru through its subsidiary SN Power.
The investment is expected to amount to $400 million.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
